    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Techniques: White </p><p></p><p>As a Reaction to being hit by a melee or ranged attack, you can attempt to pull another creature in to take your place.</p><p> Select a creature within 30 feet of you.</p><p> The creature must make a Strength saving throw against your Ninjutsu Save DC or Genjutsu Save DC.</p><p> On failure, you pull them towards you whilst also simultaneously pulling yourself to their previous position.</p><p> The target of the attack becomes this new creature.</p><p></p>",
